              <span class="lang-div" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <button class="lang-opt" onclick="setLang('pt')" id="lbtn-pt" title="Português"><span class="lang-flag">🇧🇷</span>PT</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="hero-slim-bar" id="heroSlimBar">
      <div class="hero-slim-brand" onclick="showProfileScreen()" title="Volver al perfil">
        <div class="hero-slim-dot"></div>
        <span class="hero-slim-name" id="heroSlimName">Examen de conciencia</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
        <button class="slim-menu-btn" id="slimMenuBtn" onclick="slimMenuAction()" title="Opciones">↺ Reiniciar</button>
        <div class="hero-slim-flags">
          <button class="slim-flag-btn active" id="slim-lbtn-es" onclick="setLang('es')" title="Español">🇪🇸</button>
          <div class="hero-slim-div"></div>
          <button class="slim-flag-btn" id="slim-lbtn-en" onclick="setLang('en')" title="English">🇺🇸</button>
          <div class="hero-slim-div"></div>
          <button class="slim-flag-btn" id="slim-lbtn-pt" onclick="setLang('pt')" title="Português">🇧🇷</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <aside class="side">
        <h3>Ruta del examen</h3>
        <div class="meta">
          <div class="box">
            <div class="muted small">Tiempo sugerido</div>
            <div class="timer" id="timer">25:00</div>
            <div class="controls" style="margin-top:10px">
              <button class="secondary hidden" id="startTimer" type="button">Iniciar</button>
              <button class="ghost hidden" id="pauseTimer" type="button">Pausar</button>
              <button class="ghost hidden" id="resetTimer" type="button">Reiniciar</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="box">
            <div class="muted small">Avance del recorrido</div>
            <div style="font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Lora',Georgia,serif;letter-spacing:.02em" id="progressText">0%</div>
            <div class="progress"><span id="bar"></span></div>
            <div class="small muted" style="margin-top:8px" id="progressLabel">Inicio del examen</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="callout small">
          La gravedad de un pecado no depende solo de la cantidad. También cuentan la materia, la conciencia, el consentimiento y el daño causado.
          <div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted)">Catecismo de la Iglesia Católica, nn. 1857–1859 · <a href="https://www.vatican.va/archive/catechism_sp/p3s1c1a8_sp.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Ver texto ↗</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="stepper" id="toc"></div>

        <div class="side-note app small" style="padding:0;overflow:hidden">
          <button id="installToggle" type="button" onclick="(function(){var p=document.getElementById('installPanel');var a=document.getElementById('installArrow');var open=p.style.display==='block';p.style.display=open?'none':'block';a.style.transform=open?'rotate(0deg)':'rotate(90deg)';})()" style="width:100%;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:12px 14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;border-radius:0;transform:none">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" style="flex-shrink:0;opacity:.7"><rect x="1" y="3" width="12" height="9" rx="2" stroke="#2A3340" stroke-width="1.2"/><path d="M7 1v6M5 5l2 2 2-2" stroke="#2A3340" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              <span style="font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;color:#2A3340">Instalar como app</span>
            </div>
