        step1Card1Title:'Before you begin',
        step1Card1Sub:'This is not therapy or scrupulosity. It is standing before God with truth, diligence, and peace.',
        step1Card1Body:'This is not about filling in boxes. It is about seeing yourself truthfully. Contrition is "sorrow of the soul and detestation for the sin committed, together with the resolution not to sin again" <strong>(CCC 1451)</strong>. If it is hard to feel sorrow today, ask the Lord for it. Grace is at work there too <strong>(CCC 1453)</strong>.',
