        step5Prayer:'My God, I am heartily sorry for having offended You. I detest my sins not only because by sinning I deserve the punishments established by You, but most of all because I offend You, supreme Good and worthy of all my love. I firmly resolve, with the help of Your grace, to sin no more and to avoid the occasions of sin. Amen.',
